						 <p>Idk if this counts as necro, but here goes.<br /> I really liked this for some reason (maybe it's the turtles). It's a pretty nice piece as it stands, but some exploration logs would make it even better, as it has potential. A turtle civilisation on Mars gives way to some interesting backstory possibilities.<br /> +1, though I'd really like to see the logs being made</p> 
				 	]]>
