					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6646390#post-3888323</guid>
				<title>What the shell</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6646390/scp-1565#post-3888323</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 28 Jul 2018 06:04:30 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Weryllium</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2727655</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>My first rewrite; a reimagining of ObserverSeptember's controversial Martian Turtles.</p> <p>This probably isn't what they originally intended, but it's still &quot;turtles on Mars&quot;, as per their wishes. I've mainly cut redaction, while attempting to keep the air of mystery. I hope both fans and detractors of the original can enjoy this.</p> <p>Many thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3129691&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1581636109" alt="Modern_Erasmus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3129691)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" >Modern_Erasmus</a></span> for assistance during the rewrite process and crit, and big thanks to all my crit peeps: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2887044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1581636109" alt="DrBleep" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2887044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" >DrBleep</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3187823&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1581636109" alt="CadaverCommander" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3187823)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" >CadaverCommander</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1581636109" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3938622&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1581636109" alt="The Great Hippo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3938622)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" >The Great Hippo</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1581636109" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span>.</p> <p><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Hellas_Planitia_by_the_Viking_orbiters.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Hellas_Planitia_by_the_Viking_orbiters.jpg</a> public domain</p> 
